  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/SensorKit\/SRKeyboardMetrics\/SentimentCategory\/absolutist\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T21:53:14Z\n---\n\n# SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.absolutist\n\n**Case**\n\nA mood that embodies absolutism.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\ncase absolutist\n```\n\n## Sentiments\n\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.anger**: A mood that embodies anger.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.anxiety**: A mood that embodies worrying.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.confused**: A mood that embodies confusion.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.death**: A mood that expresses death.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.down**: A mood that embodies depression.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.health**: A general concern for health.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.lowEnergy**: A mood that indicates low energy.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.positive**: A mood that embodies positivity.\n- **SRKeyboardMetrics.SentimentCategory.sad**: A mood that embodies sadness.\n\n",
